author: Y Combinator
description:
Before YC, Rishi Choudhary was working a regular 9–5, frustrated by how slow things moved and fighting to build anything new.

Now, as co-founder of Kastle (YC S24), he's able to finally build products that people really want.

And you can too. It's not too late to get your application in.

title: Founder Stories: Rishi Choudhary
